We highly recommand to activate the Looting function in General Settings => Looting & Farming options => Loot mobs => ON
We highly recommand to deactivate the Looting function in General Settings => Looting & Farming options => Loot mobs => OFF
We recommand to activate the Looting function for Pandaria in General Settings => Looting & Farming options => Loot mobs => ON
We highly recommand to deactivate the Looting function out of Pandaria in General Settings => Looting & Farming options => Loot mobs => OFF
We highly recommand to activate the Selling function while questing, in General Settings => NPCs Management - Repairer, Vendor (Selling or Buying) => Selling => ON
We also recommand to activate selling for Grey, White and Green items to avoid getting your bags full / not able to sell its content.
We highly recommand to set the Search Radius value at most to 30 yards in General Settings => Looting & Farming options => Search Radius => -30
We highly recommand to set the Search Radius value at least to 100 yards in General Settings => Looting & Farming options => Search Radius => 100+
We highly recommand to activate Ground Mount in General Settings => Mount options => Use Ground Mount => YES.
We highly recommand to deactivate Ground Mount in General Settings => Mount options => Use Ground Mount => NO.
We highly recommand to set a Ground Mount Name in General Settings => Mount options => Ground => Name of the Mount.
We highly recommand to set a Flying Mount Name in General Settings => Mount options => Flying => Name of the Mount.
We highly recommand to set the Minimum distance to use Ground Mount to 30 in General Settings => Mount options.
